====Part two: Bare-Handed Fishing====
Speak to [[Otto Godblessed]] about the barbarian [[Fishing]] methods; he will talk to you about catching fish with your arms instead of a harpoon.

Go to an area where you can harpoon [[swordfish]], [[tuna]] or [[shark]]s; the [[Fishing Guild]] and [[Catherby]] are good choices. Click on the harpoon spot as you would normally - you will catch a fish using your fingers as bait!

